Q ) Why did you choose this tech stack?
A ) I chose React for its component-based architecture.
   It helps reuse UI elements like menu cards and sections.
   React provides fast rendering using the Virtual DOM.
   CSS/Bootstrap ensures responsive design quickly.
   This stack is scalable and easy to maintain.

Q ) How would you improve this project?
A ) Add backend integration for real product data.
Implement cart and user authentication.
Use Context API or Redux for state management.
Improve performance using lazy loading.
Add testing and accessibility improvements.

Q ) How do you handle debugging?
A )  I check console errors and browser DevTools first.
Use console.log to track state and props.
Inspect components using React DevTools.
Break the problem into smaller parts.
Refer to documentation and logs to fix issues.
